		"description": "Now that Alloy uses Babel to transpile ES6 code, we should update [kitchensink-v2|https://github.com/appcelerator/kitchensink-v2] to use ES6 as well. It is our most important sample-project and should reflect the latest technologies we provide. \r\n\r\nChanges to consider\r\n- Change {{var}} to {{let}} / {{const}}\r\n- Use arrow-syntax ({{() =>}} instead of {{function()}} callback). Maybe even use promises?\r\n- Use classes instead of functions?\r\n- Add linting of possible?",
